lenders.name: Peter
lenders.loan_because:
I am a promoter and I used to live in Los Angeles, but now I am in Yuma, Arizona in a virgin Market for Urban Events.  
I am looking for a huge favor; I need people to help me get this show done. I am looking for people to invest or loan me the capital for this show for only 14 days. 
I am offering a 50% interest on any amount I get as a loan or for investment for this show. The capital plus the interest will be paid right after the show.  There is no risk involved in this show because I am getting insurance against any lost and other unforeseen things and this show will be sold out no matter what be the case.  I will pay investors at the close of the box office before we take out production cost.
Investments in the Music Industry give the investor a great opportunity to see his/her initial investment increase in a short amount of time whiles creating a huge exposure for themselves, services and products as well. In addition it’s a great business to be involved in. Mingling and meeting some of the world’s most popular music artists is at your finger tips. Concerts make money and sell products, and they do this in a timely manner. Not tying up your funds for long periods of time, consistent communication and availability to you the investor. With the economy in such a slump, why not invest in something where you can make FAST cash back on your returns and also expose your services and products if you have that. This group is very huge in this area.
lenders.occupational_info: Events promotions
